trials.eligibility_criteria:
Inclusion Criteria:

* aged between 18 and 75 years;
* remained clinically stable (respiratory symptoms and lung function parameters not exceeding normal daily variations) for 4 consecutive weeks;
* no acute upper respiratory tract infections within 4 weeks;
* 1 or more BEs within the previous 2 yea

Inclusion Criteria:

1. subjects were aged 18-80 years old;
2. a diagnosis of idiopathic or post-infective bronchiectasis was made;
3. patients had at least two exacerbations in the past year and were in a stable state for at least 4 weeks prior to the primary enrollment.

